<p>【5】《Financing and Distribution of Pharmaceuticals in the United States》July 4, 2017 https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jama/fullarticle/2627994</p>
<p>【6】《 Top U.S. pharmacies ranked by prescription drugs market share in 2019》Statistics https://www.statista.com/statistics/734171/pharmacies-ranked-by-rx-market-share-in-us/</p>
<p>【7】《年度盘点：2019中国药企在美获批ANDA排行榜》 药智网</p>
